This application is based on AWS Services. To better involved into this problem, I would recommend you to get some general idea about AWS Services.

Service/API used in this project
1.	AWS Lambda
2.	Amazon S3
3.	AWS IAM
4.	Amazon Cognito
5.	Amazon CloudWatch
6.	Amazon Rekognition
7.	Amazon Translate

Lambda is the core of this application. And here are some references you can take a look at about Lambda
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xmacMfbrG28&t=746s
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QdzV04T_kec&t=2649s
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TOn0xhev0Uk

